One Thousand Island Lake Resort)

166
00:15:43,626 --> 00:15:44,267
Sir, this way.

167
00:15:44,667 --> 00:15:46,226
- Come on, sir, this way.
- Enough.

168
00:15:46,466 --> 00:15:47,792
- Come on.
- Feishao.

169
00:15:47,792 --> 00:15:50,307
Food is ready. Grab a seat.

170
00:15:52,027 --> 00:15:53,866
- Grab a seat.
- So many dishes.

171
00:15:54,826 --> 00:15:56,307
Send a photo to Zhu.

172
00:15:57,746 --> 00:16:00,027
- Sit in front of me.
- Thanks.

173
00:16:00,027 --> 00:16:02,187
- Sit here.
- I'll be next to Doudou.

174
00:16:03,147 --> 00:16:03,746
Xiaoxing.

175
00:16:04,947 --> 00:16:06,787
- Where do I sit?
- Sit anywhere you want.

176
00:16:06,787 --> 00:16:07,787
- Really?
- Sit here.

177
00:16:07,787 --> 00:16:10,547
- Come here.
- Zheng, I want to sit next to you.

178
00:16:10,826 --> 00:16:14,626
Guys, they make great fish here.

179
00:16:14,746 --> 00:16:17,466
It's still midday. Let's dig in.

180
00:16:17,586 --> 00:16:20,586
- Then let's drive the off-roader, okay?
- Alright.

181
00:16:20,667 --> 00:16:21,947
- Here.
- This is tender.

182
00:16:22,346 --> 00:16:24,027
- What's this?
- Tofu.

183
00:16:24,106 --> 00:16:26,746
- Where is the fish?
- Have some fish.

184
00:16:28,226 --> 00:16:29,866
- It's good.
- Is it?

185
00:16:31,027 --> 00:16:31,986
Thank you.

186
00:16:32,826 --> 00:16:34,746
- It's so nice.
- Dig in.

187
00:16:40,106 --> 00:16:43,027
Doudou, can you
put an extra bed in your room?

188
00:16:44,907 --> 00:16:46,226
- Yeah, why?
- Thanks.

189
00:16:46,826 --> 00:16:50,187
Let Xiaoxing share your room.
It's livelier like this.

190
00:16:51,387 --> 00:16:52,746
What about Sheng?

191
00:16:55,187 --> 00:16:58,907
She's scared of the dark.
How is she going to sleep alone?

192
00:17:00,826 --> 00:17:03,307
Yeah, they are fine together.

193
00:17:03,387 --> 00:17:05,306
Why would she squeeze at my place?

194
00:17:09,026 --> 00:17:13,147
Doudou, here. Have some fish heads.
It's good for the brain.

195
00:17:13,147 --> 00:17:18,026
Are you so close to Xiaoxing now?
You're arranging for her accommodation?

196
00:17:25,266 --> 00:17:28,066
- Cousin, want some fish soup?
- Yeah, thanks.

197
00:17:28,266 --> 00:17:28,907
You're welcome.

198
00:17:35,746 --> 00:17:42,827
- Isn't he taking good care of her?
- H-He's fine. There's a long way to go.

199
00:17:44,786 --> 00:17:45,546
Have a shrimp.

200
00:17:48,026 --> 00:17:49,026
What's going on?

201
00:17:49,427 --> 00:17:51,947
- Are you eating it or not?
- Yeah.

202
00:17:52,107 --> 00:17:54,627
You got it for me.
Of course, I'd eat it.

203
00:17:58,867 --> 00:18:00,706
It's nice. Try it.

204
00:18:03,147 --> 00:18:03,986
Have some meat.

205
00:18:10,147 --> 00:18:12,587
- Slowly. Be careful of the bones.
- Let me teach you.

206
00:18:13,867 --> 00:18:14,587
Teach me.

207
00:18:16,066 --> 00:18:17,627
Why's the watermelon so sweet?

208
00:18:18,907 --> 00:18:23,986
- Mr. Mu, have a pineapple. Be sour.
- Let me peel a shrimp for you.

209
00:18:24,506 --> 00:18:28,147
Come on, you didn't remove the shell
or clean the sand vein.

210
00:18:28,627 --> 00:18:31,506
Loners help loners. Sure.
Peel one for me. I'll eat it.

211
00:18:31,667 --> 00:18:33,147
- Alright, wait.
- Seriously.

212
00:18:36,226 --> 00:18:38,786
- I'm a VIP. I know everything.
- Alright.

213
00:18:39,026 --> 00:18:40,947
- Take this one.
- I'll ask you for help.

214
00:18:42,947 --> 00:18:49,147
Guys, this is off-roader driving,
the most special event here.

215
00:18:49,147 --> 00:18:52,427
- Nice cars.
- Why is it the most special?

216
00:18:53,306 --> 00:18:57,627
The route is complicated.
It's very thrilling. Take a look.

217
00:18:57,746 --> 00:19:02,827
The mountain road
is narrow, bumpy, and lengthy.

218
00:19:02,986 --> 00:19:06,827
- It's one of a kind.
- Not bad.

219
00:19:06,947 --> 00:19:08,827
You make it sound like
we're here to suffer.

220
00:19:08,947 --> 00:19:11,026
Aren't we here to enjoy the excitement?

221
00:19:11,147 --> 00:19:15,568
Let's form groups of two.
Couples should share a car.

222
00:19:15,706 --> 00:19:18,387
It's a perfect chance
to get closer to each other.

223
00:19:19,546 --> 00:19:24,147
There's only one couple.
The others can team up as they want.

224
00:19:27,427 --> 00:19:30,306
- Only one couple.
- Enough.

225
00:19:32,947 --> 00:19:36,587
I prepared handkerchiefs for you.
It's going to be very dusty.

226
00:19:36,706 --> 00:19:39,627
And it's a long way. Cover your face.

227
00:19:39,867 --> 00:19:44,226
- Lady first. One for each. Xiaoxing.
- You're very considerate today.

228
00:19:44,306 --> 00:19:46,306
- He became so thoughtful.
- Caring.

229
00:19:46,947 --> 00:19:48,187
- The nice guy.
- I want this one.

230
00:19:48,306 --> 00:19:49,706
- Come on, Sheng.
- This one.

231
00:19:49,986 --> 00:19:52,627
- Come on, pick one.
- Guys, pick yours.

232
00:19:53,147 --> 00:19:54,706
I'll show you how to wear it.

233
00:19:55,147 --> 00:19:57,506
Mine is too colorful. Let's exchange.

234
00:19:57,506 --> 00:20:00,427
- You know how to do it? Amazing.
- Let me help.

235
00:20:01,587 --> 00:20:03,546
- Here.
- Help Xiaoxing.

236
00:20:06,187 --> 00:20:08,506
- Give it to me, honey.
- Thanks, Doudou.

237
00:20:09,546 --> 00:20:14,066
It's going to be dusty on the road.
Just leave your eyes out.

238
00:20:16,746 --> 00:20:18,387
- Is it too tight?
- It's alright.

239
00:20:20,066 --> 00:20:22,266
- Loners help loners.
- Sure.

240
00:20:22,466 --> 00:20:23,746
- Help me.
- Let me.

241
00:20:23,867 --> 00:20:25,986
- Come on.
- Come on, Feishao. Let me help.

242
00:20:25,986 --> 00:20:26,427
Come on.

243
00:20:28,546 --> 00:20:29,347
Tell me if it's tight.

244
00:20:31,387 --> 00:20:31,907
Is it tight?

245
00:20:34,026 --> 00:20:35,746
- Alright.
- Alright.

246
00:20:38,347 --> 00:20:39,827
- Get in the car.
- Thanks, Doudou.

247
00:20:41,427 --> 00:20:41,947
