Three shots. Whoever scores higher wins.

496
00:36:55,472 --> 00:36:58,476
Track No.1. Track No.2.
Start with Track No.1.

497
00:37:00,515 --> 00:37:01,035
Go for it.

498
00:37:01,316 --> 00:37:03,996
Let him win, okay? Don't steal his show.

499
00:37:04,195 --> 00:37:06,115
No way. I have to teach him a lesson.

500
00:37:08,595 --> 00:37:09,796
I'll let him win
by one point for each shot.

501
00:37:17,756 --> 00:37:20,876
- Eighth ring.
- Zhou Zheng, eighth ring.

502
00:37:23,472 --> 00:37:25,876
- Let's compete with them in secret.
- Alright, good luck.

503
00:37:26,796 --> 00:37:29,115
- Mo Bai, take photos for me.
- Coming.

504
00:37:29,436 --> 00:37:31,635
Let's see what
the pro player is capable of.

505
00:37:34,276 --> 00:37:40,756
Don't let me down, Juemei Shayi.
You'd better start dating her.

506
00:37:43,796 --> 00:37:45,756
Wang Ke, seventh ring.

507
00:37:46,864 --> 00:37:48,356
Juemei is one point ahead.

508
00:37:51,316 --> 00:37:51,836
Fifth ring.

509
00:37:53,635 --> 00:37:54,796
Let me hit the bull's eye.

510
00:37:59,075 --> 00:38:01,996
- Make some noise.
- Alright!

511
00:38:06,916 --> 00:38:08,916
Zhou Zheng, fifth ring.

512
00:38:10,396 --> 00:38:13,796
- It was windy.
- I can't lose too obviously.

513
00:38:13,796 --> 00:38:15,235
Aim for the fifth ring.

514
00:38:16,316 --> 00:38:18,064
- Fifth ring.
- Fine.

515
00:38:19,555 --> 00:38:23,635
- Juemei, is that all you've got?
- Cut the crap. Hurry up.

516
00:38:23,876 --> 00:38:26,595
Wang Ke, it's time
for you to turn the game around.

517
00:38:28,635 --> 00:38:30,256
Will you make it?

518
00:38:34,276 --> 00:38:38,128
Wang Ke, sixth ring. It's a draw.

519
00:38:38,635 --> 00:38:42,515
- I told you the fifth ring.
- It flew up a bit, okay?

520
00:38:47,075 --> 00:38:47,836
Seventh ring.

521
00:38:58,956 --> 00:39:02,356
- Eighth ring.
- Zhou Zheng, eighth ring.

522
00:39:03,035 --> 00:39:04,436
Impressive, Mr. Zhou.

523
00:39:04,436 --> 00:39:09,195
This is the final shot.
Wang Ke is under huge pressure.

524
00:39:09,276 --> 00:39:11,276
Stop it. I'm so nervous.

525
00:39:13,916 --> 00:39:18,316
Let's see how he does in the final shot.

526
00:39:24,396 --> 00:39:27,916
Wang Ke, seventh ring.
I hereby announce the result.

527
00:39:27,916 --> 00:39:31,876
The winner is Zhou Zheng with 21 points.

528
00:39:35,316 --> 00:39:37,796
- Zheng, you're amazing.
- Careful.

529
00:39:37,796 --> 00:39:43,155
Way to go, Juemei. You defeated
a semi-professional so easily.

530
00:39:43,155 --> 00:39:46,515
- Semi-professional? You're an amateur.
- Too easy.

531
00:39:46,555 --> 00:39:48,595
You were even stepping on the line.

532
00:39:49,316 --> 00:39:53,316
- You're right, Mr. Zhou.
- Three, two, one. Let go.

533
00:39:59,195 --> 00:39:59,876
Tenth ring.

534
00:40:02,075 --> 00:40:03,956
- Amazing.
- Practice with me.

535
00:40:04,515 --> 00:40:06,155
- Let me try it.
- Alright.

536
00:40:06,155 --> 00:40:07,555
- Try it.
- Tenth ring.

537
00:40:07,555 --> 00:40:09,276
- Who did it?
- Really?

538
00:40:09,276 --> 00:40:11,876
Sheng? Sheng, was that you?

539
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:14,155
Five, seven, ten.

540
00:40:15,155 --> 00:40:19,075
- She got 22 points in three shots.
- That's good.

541
00:40:20,476 --> 00:40:24,555
- You're amazing, Sheng.
- Sheng, I'm so proud of you.

542
00:40:25,796 --> 00:40:27,155
You did well.

543
00:40:28,916 --> 00:40:30,635
You're the champion.

544
00:40:30,956 --> 00:40:38,996
- Champion!
- Champion!

545
00:40:39,515 --> 00:40:42,316
So talent matters a lot, right?

546
00:40:43,075 --> 00:40:45,155
Gifted. Look at them.

547
00:40:45,675 --> 00:40:46,195
Champion!

548
00:41:00,595 --> 00:41:02,675
Are we having dinner together?
What would you like?

549
00:41:05,075 --> 00:41:09,515
I'm not sure. Let's see what there is.

550
00:41:09,916 --> 00:41:10,675
You have a date?

551
00:41:12,075 --> 00:41:18,876
No, Juemei doesn't have an appetite.
So we're getting some special cuisine.

552
00:41:20,316 --> 00:41:22,096
Special cuisine.

553
00:41:24,075 --> 00:41:26,876
- Not so special.
- Alright, you're free tonight.

554
00:41:26,996 --> 00:41:28,496
Don't come back. Bye.

555
00:41:46,396 --> 00:41:52,555
(Someone had fun shooting arrows
with his wife, ignoring everyone else.)

556
00:41:52,555 --> 00:41:58,306
(Mo Bai, please update more about "someone".
Mr. Qiang is so talented!)

557
00:42:09,876 --> 00:42:10,916
Want to take a nap?

558
00:42:12,876 --> 00:42:14,756
I thought we were going to have food.

559
00:42:46,499 --> 00:42:51,107
♪There is a voice
that soaks the green plums♪

560
00:42:52,451 --> 00:42:56,899
♪There is a voice
that wrinkles the blue sky♪

561
00:42:58,329 --> 00:43:02,618
♪Shedding an invisible spring rain♪

562
00:43:02,618 --> 00:43:08,317
♪The world is drunk at a timid moment♪

563
00:43:10,143 --> 00:43:15,011
♪We talk and laugh
as if we are holding hands♪

564
00:43:16,451 --> 00:43:22,499
♪We stay silent
like falling behind the sunset♪

565
00:43:22,499 --> 00:43:26,595
♪That moment is still lingering♪

566
00:43:26,595 --> 00:43:32,452
♪When our eyes meet,
all vanish into nothing♪

567
00:43:59,171 --> 00:44:05,217
♪You flow through my heart like a river♪

568
00:44:05,891 --> 00:44:10,979
♪Echoing with the constant gentleness
of the bright moon♪

569
00:44:11,779 --> 00:44:14,947
♪Looking back
among fleeting and everlasting moments♪

570
00:44:14,947 --> 00:44:17,603
♪We embrace as we look around♪

571
00:44:17,955 --> 00:44:22,691
♪Each sound is a promise of forever
to a lifetime♪

572
00:44:23,299 --> 00:44:29,251
♪You linger in my dreams
countless times♪

573
00:44:29,891 --> 00:44:35,203
♪Whenever I see you,
my heart flutters a thousand times♪

574
00:44:35,203 --> 00:44:39,044
♪Birds fly past spring and autumn
once again♪

575
00:44:39,044 --> 00:44:42,040
♪The splendid world still remains♪

576
00:44:42,652 --> 00:44:46,339
♪Gifting us freedom♪

577
00:44:46,339 --> 00:44:50,758
♪We ferment each other into wine♪

578
00:44:52,444 --> 00:44:58,115
♪Within the intoxication, I can feel♪

579
00:44:58,467 --> 00:45:02,627
♪Your voice drifts across my heart♪

580
00:45:02,627 --> 00:45:09,891
♪Drifting through my life with no end♪
